{
  "texts": [
    "It includes calculating the inner product matrix of local features of two-point cloud.",
    "This method fully improves the characteristics of source point cloud and can effectively handle the registration of point cloud with large initial Angle.",
    "The method then uses 2DCNN to further extract the features and extend them to one-dimensional tensors.",
    "Finally, a scaling factor is introduced at the end of the",
    "Method of disregarding non-overlapping regions."
  ]
}